Class MixedCollection

java.lang.Object
au.csiro.pathling.fhirpath.collection.Collection
au.csiro.pathling.fhirpath.collection.mixed.MixedCollection
Direct Known Subclasses:
ChoiceElementCollection
public abstract class MixedCollection extends Collection
Represents a polymorphic collection, which can be resolved to any one of a number of data types.

John Grimes
